Are you clueless as to why your relationship has ended abruptly, without warning? We spoke to men on why they called it quits and lied to their exes on the real reason  Experiencing a breakup is inevitable (unless you live in Mars). We have had a first date, had an incredible connection, and then somewhere along the line we discover something is wrong with the relationship and the only solution is to part ways.  



